📘 Essential Reading

https://beej.us/guide/bgnet/

Legendary beginner-to-advanced guide for BSD sockets.

https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man7/epoll.7.html

Shows why poll() or epoll() is used, edge vs level triggering, caveats.

💡 Reference Implementations

https://github.com/nginx/nginx/tree/master/src/event

Look at ngx_event.c, ngx_event_accept.c – very clean modular loop.


https://github.com/libevent/libevent

Production-ready event loop. Great inspiration even if you’re not using it.